{"tid":1150065,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"誤入尖沙咀……有感","createTime":"2019-05-11T14:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T14:53:41.000Z","uid":73878,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ad95c4f7562e485ce3cf2cb5fee954cc7ba7c72","tid":1150065,"uid":73878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"作為一個香港人，我已經數以年計未敢踏足尖沙咀，特別是Soho,太空館一帶<br />\n<br />\n是日因為我個唔生性嘅細佬，無攞屋企鎖匙而要我送條匙，深入虎穴去海運附近俾佢。<br />\n<br />\n由西鐵一出，我就到左郵局附近個出口，諗住果邊條應該咁多&ldquo;人&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n點知一出個出口就 心知不妙， 我完全唔記得咗今日係sogo大減價嘅日子， 出到個出口只係見到一地嘅傳單，<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xjknD9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xjknD9.jpg&h=811fafb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 仲有一啲 偉大嘅香港恩客， 佢哋對住個喼就彷彿好似啲喪屍對住人類 一樣吞噬， 露出 欲求不滿，目露凶光嘅表情<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R93dHEN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR93dHEN.jpg&h=b5f28ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好不容易先 跨過 呢啲喼 避開橫衝直撞嘅喪屍， 終於畀我去到 半島酒店嘅對面準備要過馬路嘅時候， 我又睇到另一群嘅喪屍正向sogo嘅方向要衝過嚟<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vufoksi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVufoksi.jpg&h=0662eb75&s={SIZE}\" /> 係呢一刻 馬路中間嘅安全島已經不再安全， 中間夾住正要過嚟 亦都有準備離開 嘅喪屍們<br />\n<br />\n我再抬頭望下太空館嘅方向又係另一群<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eFiEDeG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeFiEDeG.jpg&h=f0b1501b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來而家 要玩biohazard， 根本就唔需要再靠vr， 你只需要 向尖沙咀出發你就有親身嘅體驗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係覺得身為一個香港人 我係唔應該存在喺尖沙咀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e8cfc5fe2fa293ee60ddddf8948732654e866c","tid":1150065,"uid":17075,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"不嬲最憎去尖沙咀同旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇咩事唔會去個頭"},{"pid":"a2a38ba1ebdec198dd2d112f4d6ac8a68595e399","tid":1150065,"uid":184233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀都叫香港? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7305b5670362be79d07a36434d49f31ae11461","tid":1150065,"uid":80503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"樓主衰咩坐左咁多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐到相都唔識影"},{"pid":"0957adf50fb033bcf72b7224999e55a6c6ccaed5","tid":1150065,"uid":73878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"我以前去尖沙嘴，覺得好似返左大陸咁，我都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今日去咗尖沙咀喺邊咗喪屍嘅世界"},{"pid":"72503636641c95d9798f46b32df4e1264dc21e2c","tid":1150065,"uid":52059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:53:41.000Z","msg":"屯門v city都係丫<br />\n西鐵一出閘就成堆人、喼"}]}